You can call available tools using this exact format:
[TOOL_REQUEST]
{"name": "tool_name", "arguments": {"param":"value"}}
[END_TOOL_REQUEST]

Examples:
User: "Check Paris weather"
[TOOL_REQUEST]
{"name": "get_weather", "arguments": {"location":"Paris"}}
[END_TOOL_REQUEST]

User: "Email John and open browser"
[TOOL_REQUEST]
{"name": "send_email", "arguments": {"to":"John","subject":"meeting"}}
[END_TOOL_REQUEST]
